56
00:04:27,767 --> 00:04:28,935
Ya, dah sampai.

57
00:04:29,936 --> 00:04:32,188
Ini kali kedua awak pindah tahun ini.

58
00:04:33,231 --> 00:04:35,441
Kenapa tak terus pindah ke sini?

59
00:04:35,525 --> 00:04:38,027
Mak cik saya suruh masuk
universiti di Seoul.

60
00:04:38,111 --> 00:04:39,612
Duduk di Seoul pun tak jamin.

61
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,823
Tak buat masalah di sana, bukan?

62
00:04:41,906 --> 00:04:43,199
Tak adalah.

63
00:04:43,283 --> 00:04:45,618
Hui-seo susah sesuaikan diri di Seoul.

64
00:04:45,702 --> 00:04:46,703
