165
00:16:34,702 --> 00:16:37,329
Seragam sukan berharga, senior tak derma.

166
00:16:37,413 --> 00:16:38,956
Mereka pakai sampai lusuh.

167
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:42,459
Ini seluar magis. Muat semua saiz.

168
00:16:43,335 --> 00:16:44,878
Mesti muat elok.

169
00:16:44,962 --> 00:16:47,089
Memang padu. Selesa pun ya. Tengok!

170
00:16:47,172 --> 00:16:49,842
Hei, janganlah!

171
00:16:49,925 --> 00:16:51,010
Terkejut saya.

172
00:16:52,469 --> 00:16:53,804
Saya nak tunjuk saya pakai.

173
00:16:55,014 --> 00:16:56,890
Terima kasih.

174
