<i>Kimchi </i>buatan nenek awak.

175
00:17:05,482 --> 00:17:06,942
Ini barang berharga.

176
00:17:09,570 --> 00:17:11,030
Waktu bertukar barang,

177
00:17:11,113 --> 00:17:14,450
